<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="tubitak-2211-a-scholarship-program-2025-current-information">TÜBİTAK 2211-A Scholarship Program: 2025 Current Information</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong><strong>TÜBİTAK </strong></strong>is Turkey&#8217;s largest funding agency for science and technology. The 2211-A program provides great financial support to students starting their PhD studies.<br>And yes, good news: Foreign students can also apply!</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><a href="https://tubitak.gov.tr/tr/burslar/lisansustu/egitim-burs-programlari/2211-yurt-ici-doktora-burs-programlari" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TÜBİTAK Official Website</a>, so be sure to follow the application dates.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-much-is-the-tubitak-2211-a-scholarship-amount">How Much is the TÜBİTAK 2211-A Scholarship Amount?</h3>



