<h2 class="wp-block-heading wp-block-paragraph">How Much Are PhD Scholarships in Turkey in 2025?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">PhD scholarships in Turkey have been updated as of 2025, taking into account exchange rate increases and changes in living costs.<br>In other words, funding is much more attractive than in previous years.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="phd-supports-provided-by-universities">PhD Supports Provided by Universities</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Some public universities in Turkey offer PhD students the opportunity to work on research projects or in assistant positions.<br>This support is not a direct &#8220;PhD scholarship&#8221;, but a form of salary.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The estimated USD equivalent of research assistant salaries for 2025 will be as follows:</p>


