<td>Project Based Support</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</figure>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In addition to these salaries, some universities may also provide students with meal cards or dormitory accommodation support.<br>But the practice of each faculty and department may be different.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="special-institution-and-foundation-scholarships">Special Institution and Foundation Scholarships</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Some major Turkish foundations also offer doctoral scholarships to foreign students.<br>Featured:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Vehbi Koç Foundation Scholarships</strong></li>



<li><strong>TEV (Turkish Education Foundation) Graduate and Doctoral Scholarships</strong></li>



