<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="city-transportation-and-food-expenses">City Transportation and Food Expenses</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">City transportation in Turkey is quite affordable. Many cities offer special discount transportation cards for students. The average monthly transportation card costs around <strong>$60</strong>.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Food will be an important part of your budget. A meal at a university dining hall costs <strong>$2 &#8211; $5</strong>. If you want to eat out at a restaurant, you can expect to spend an average of <strong>$4 &#8211; $15</strong> for one meal.</p>


