 destekleri hakkında güncel bilgiler. Öğrenciler için ücretsiz yurtlar ve destekler seni bekliyor. Hemen keşfet!","name":"Türkiye&#039;de Barınma Bursları 2025: 6 Fırsatla Kolay Konaklama","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/turkiye-barinma-burslari-konaklama/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/turkiye-barinma-burslari-konaklama/#webpage"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/housing-scholarships-and-accommodation-support-in-turkey.webp"},"inLanguage":"tr","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/turkiye-barinma-burslari-konaklama/#webpage"}}]}]}'), '$.content_html', '<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Barınma bursları</strong>, Türkiye’ye üniversite okumaya gelen uluslararası öğrenciler için en çok aranan desteklerden biri. Çünkü ilk stres kaynağı genellikle konaklama oluyor: Nerede kalacağım? Kaç para? Yurt mu ev mi? Neyse ki, Türkiye bu konuda gerçekten cömert. Özellikle devlet destekli burslar ve konaklama yardımları, birçok öğrencinin barınma sorununu çözüyor. Bu yazıda hem ücretsiz kalabileceğin seçenekleri hem de destek alabileceğin kurumları tek tek ele aldım.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="turkiyede-uluslararasi-ogrencilere-sunulan-barinma-secenekleri">Türkiye’de Uluslararası Öğrencilere Sunulan Barınma Seçenekleri</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Türkiye’de öğrencilerin en sık tercih ettiği konaklama türlerini üç ana grupta toplayabiliriz:</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>1. Devlet Yurtları (KYK):</strong> Gençlik ve Spor Bakanlığı’na bağlı yurtlardır. En ucuz ve güvenli seçeneklerden biridir.<br><strong>2. Özel Yurtlar:</strong> Fiyatları daha yüksektir ama genellikle daha modern imkanlar sunar.<br><strong>3. Kiralık Ev/Paylaşımlı Daireler:</strong> Daha özgür bir yaşam isteyen öğrenciler için idealdir.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="barinma-turleri-ve-ortalama-aylik-maliyetler-2025">Barınma Türleri ve Ortalama Aylık Maliyetler (2025)</h3>



<figure class="wp-block-table"><table class="has-fixed-layout"><thead><tr><th>Konaklama Türü</th><th>Ortalama Aylık Maliyet (USD)</th><th>Notlar</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>KYK Devlet Yurdu</td><td>13 – 40</td><td>Ucuz ama sınırlı kontenjan</td></tr><tr><td>Özel Yurt</td><td>66 – 263</td><td>Şehre ve hizmete göre çok değişken</td></tr><tr><td>Kiralık Ev</td><td>105 – 790</td><td>İstanbul ve Ankara’da fiyatlar çok yüksek</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow">
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Daha fazla bilgi ve şehir bazlı yurt listelerine ulaşmak için <a class="" href="https://kygm.gsb.gov.tr/yurtmudurlukleri" target="_blank" rel="noopener">KYK Yurt Müdürlükleri sayfasını</a> ziyaret edebilirsin.</p>
</blockquote>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="devlet-tarafindan-saglanan-konaklama-burslari-ve-destekler">Devlet Tarafından Sağlanan Barınma Bursları ve Destekler</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Türkiye’de devlet sadece eğitim bursu vermiyor, konaklama konusunda da ciddi destekler sağlıyor. En önemlisi <strong>KYK yurtları</strong>, bazı öğrencilere tamamen ücretsiz sunulabiliyor.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="en-bilinen-devlet-destekleri">En Bilinen Devlet Destekleri:</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>KYK Ücretsiz Yurt Hakkı:</strong> Türkiye Bursları kazanan öğrencilere sağlanır.</li>



<li><strong>Barınma Yardımı:</strong> Aile ve Sosyal Hizmetler Bakanlığı aracılığıyla belirli şartları taşıyan öğrencilere yapılır.</li>



<li><strong>Afet Durumu Desteği:</strong> Deprem, sel gibi afetlerde mağdur olan öğrencilere geçici konaklama sağlanabilir.</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="kimler-faydalanabilir">Kimler Faydalanabilir?</h3>



<ol class="wp-block-list">
<li>Türkiye Bursları ile kabul alan öğrenciler</li>



<li>Sosyal yardım kriterlerine uygun uluslararası öğrenciler</li>



<li>Belirli şehirlerde üniversite kazanan ve KYK yurdu çıkmayan öğrenciler</li>
</ol>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Detaylı bilgi için <a class="" href="https://gsb.gov.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Gençlik ve Spor Bakanlığı</a> sitesini inceleyebilirsin.</p>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="vakif-ve-ozel-kuruluslarin-konaklama-yardimlari">Vakıf ve Özel Kuruluşların Konaklama Yardımları</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Devlet dışında da birçok vakıf ve kurum, öğrencilere barınma desteği sağlıyor. Bazıları doğrudan yurt sunarken, bazıları konaklama bursu şeklinde maddi yardımda bulunuyor.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="one-cikan-vakiflar-ve-kuruluslar">Öne Çıkan Vakıflar ve Kuruluşlar:</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Ensar Vakfı:</strong> İstanbul ve Ankara’da erkek öğrencilere yurt imkanı sunar.</li>



<li><strong>TÜRGEV:</strong> Kız öğrencilere yönelik modern yurtlar işletmektedir.</li>



<li><strong>İstanbul Büyükşehir Belediyesi (İBB):</strong> Öğrencilere yurt bursu ve kira desteği sağlar.</li>



<li><strong>Kızılay:</strong> Bazı şehirlerde sosyal destek kapsamında konaklama yardımı yapabiliyor.</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="konaklama-yardimi-veren-kurumlar-listesi-2025">Konaklama Yardımı Veren Kurumlar Listesi (2025)</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><a class="" href="https://turkiyemaarif.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Türkiye Maarif Vakfı</strong></a>: Uluslararası öğrenciler için Türkiye’de barınma ve okul imkanı sağlayan global bir eğitim kuruluşudur.</li>



<li><a class="" href="https://www.kizilay.org.tr" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Türk Kızılayı</strong></a>: Afet durumlarında ve ihtiyaç sahibi öğrencilere yönelik barınma ve sosyal destekler sunar.</li>



<li><a class="" href="https://www.ibb.istanbul" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>İstanbul Büyükşehir Belediyesi (İBB)</strong></a>: Üniversite öğrencilerine yönelik yurt bursları ve kira destekleri sağlar.</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Her kurumun başvuru şartları farklı; bazıları sadece belirli şehirlerde, bazıları ise sadece belirli fakültelerde okuyanlara destek veriyor. Bu yüzden başvuru öncesi detayları dikkatlice okumakta fayda var.</p>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="universite-yurtlari-mi-ozel-yurtlar-mi-karar-sureci">Üniversite Yurtları mı, Özel Yurtlar mı? Karar Süreci</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Türkiye’ye ilk geldiğimde yurt meselesi beni en çok zorlayan şey olmuştu. KYK yurduna başvurdum ama çıkmadı, özel yurtlar da pahalıydı. Kiralık ev mi, oda mı, yoksa başka şehirdeki bir yurda mı başvurmalıyım derken kafam iyice karışmıştı.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Eğer sen de böyle bir ikilemdesin, bu karşılaştırma işini biraz kolaylaştırsın:</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="yurt-turleri-karsilastirmasi">Yurt Türleri Karşılaştırması</h3>



<figure class="wp-block-table"><table class="has-fixed-layout"><thead><tr><th>Kriter</th><th>KYK Devlet Yurdu</th><th>Özel Yurt</th><th>Kiralık Ev</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Fiyat</td><td>Düşük</td><td>Orta &#8211; Yüksek</td><td>Yüksek</td></tr><tr><td>Güvenlik</td><td>Yüksek</td><td>Yüksek</td><td>Değişken</td></tr><tr><td>Özgürlük</td><td>Kısıtlı</td><td>Orta</td><td>Yüksek</td></tr><tr><td>Kapsam</td><td>Yemek + Temizlik</td><td>Çoğunlukla yemekli</td><td>Kendi başına</td></tr><tr><td>Barınma Bursu Geçerliliği</td><td>Evet</td><td>Kuruma göre değişir</td><td>Nadiren geçerli</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Karar verirken önce hangi tür barınma bursları senin durumuna uyuyor buna bakman gerekiyor. Çünkü bazı burslar yalnızca KYK yurtlarında geçerli, bazıları ise sadece özel yurtlarla anlaşmalı.</p>



<blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow">
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Yurtlar dışında evde kalmayı düşünen öğrenciler için şehir, mahalle ve kira koşulları gibi birçok detayı araştırmak şart. Özellikle büyük şehirlerde kiralar ciddi farklılık gösterebilir. <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/">Türkiye&#8217;de Ev Kiralama Rehberi: Uluslararası Öğrenciler İçin İpuçları </a>yazımız, sürece hazırlıklı başlaman için ideal bir kaynak.</p>
</blockquote>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="barinma-maliyetleri-ve-burslarla-nasil-dengelenir">Barınma Maliyetleri ve Burslarla Nasıl Dengelenir?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">İstanbul’da bir odanın kirası 2025 itibarıyla <strong>yaklaşık 158 USD</strong>&#8216;ye kadar çıkabiliyor. Öğrenci bütçesiyle bu nasıl karşılanır dersen, cevabı barınma bursları ve iyi planlama. İşin püf noktası, hem destekleri takip etmek hem de harcamaları kontrollü yapmak.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="maliyeti-dengelemek-icin-oneriler">Maliyeti Dengelemek İçin Öneriler:</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Barınma burslarına başvur:</strong> Her sene Türkiye Bursları dışında İBB, çeşitli vakıflar ve üniversiteler özel burslar açıklıyor.</li>



<li><strong>Paylaşımlı daire seç:</strong> Evde bir ya da iki arkadaşla kalmak maliyeti üçe böler.</li>



<li><strong>İndirimli KYK yurtları:</strong> Bazı şehirlerde daha uygun fiyatlı KYK yurtları var, kontenjanları erken doluyor.</li>



<li><strong>Erken başvur, yer kap:</strong> Yaz tatilinde yurt başvurularını kaçırmamak büyük avantaj sağlar.</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Şunu net söyleyebilirim: Barınma bursları sayesinde, Türkiye’de ciddi şekilde kira ödemeden üniversite okuyan çok sayıda uluslararası öğrenci var. Yani bu destekler sadece sembolik değil, gerçekten hayat kurtarıyor.</p>



<blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow">
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Bazı öğrenciler özel ya da devlet yurtlarında kalmak yerine ev kiralamayı tercih ediyor. Bu durumda maliyeti düşürmek için en yaygın yöntem paylaşımlı evlerde kalmak. Eğer bu yaşam tarzı sana uygunsa, <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/">Türkiye&#8217;de Ev Arkadaşı Bulma ve Paylaşımlı Konaklama İmkanları</a> yazısında işini kolaylaştıracak birçok ipucu bulabilirsin.</p>
</blockquote>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="simdi-basvur-konaklamani-guvenceye-al">Şimdi Başvur, Konaklamanı Güvenceye Al!</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Eğer Türkiye’ye yeni geleceksen veya hali hazırda eğitimine burada devam ediyorsan, <em>barınma bursları</em> için başvuru takvimini kaçırmamalısın. Pek çok burs sadece bir dönemlik açık oluyor ve başvuru süresi çok kısa. Bu fırsatları kaçırmamak için RoadtoStudy sayfamızdan duyuruları takip edebilirsin.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="harekete-gecmeden-once-yapman-gerekenler">Harekete Geçmeden Önce Yapman Gerekenler:</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Hangi şehirde okuyacaksan oradaki yurtları araştır</li>



<li>Barınma bursları için gerekli belgeleri hazırlamaya şimdiden başla</li>



<li>Başvuru şartlarına dikkat et: Yaş, bölüm, vatandaşlık durumu gibi detaylar önemli</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Barınma bursları, sadece maddi değil, psikolojik bir güven hissi de sağlar. Kalacak yerin hazırsa, yeni bir ülkeye alışmak çok daha kolay olur. Sen de hemen harekete geç, konaklamanı şansa bırakma.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-04-30T10:05:13Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T18:55:56Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/housing-scholarships-and-accommodation-support-in-turkey.webp","alt":"Student reviewing housing scholarship documents in a modest student apartment.","title":"housing-scholarships-and-accommodation-support-in-turkey"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'tr' AND "slug" = 'turkiye-barinma-burslari-konaklama' );
UPDATE "ec_posts" SET "source_seo" = '{"title":"Meal Scholarships in Turkey 2025: How to Apply?","description":"A guide for students seeking food scholarships in Turkey in 2025: Who''s eligible, how to apply, what to do after winning? Read now!","robots":"follow, index, max-snippet:-1, max-video-preview:-1, max-image-preview:large","ogTitle":"Meal Scholarships in Turkey 2025: How to Apply?","ogDescription":"A guide for students seeking food scholarships in Turkey in 2025: Who''s eligible, how to apply, what to do after winning? Read now!","ogImage":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/meal-scholarships-in-turkey-2025-how-to-apply-1024x772.webp","twitterCard":"summary_large_image","twitterTitle":"Meal Scholarships in Turkey 2025: How to Apply?","twitterDescription":"A guide for students seeking food scholarships in Turkey in 2025: Who''s eligible, how to apply, what to do after winning? Read now!","canonicalPath":"/en/turkey-meal-scholarships/","hreflang":[{"hreflang":"tr","href":"/turkiye-yemek-burslari/"},{"hreflang":"en","href":"/en/turkey-meal-scholarships/"}],"jsonLd":[{"@context":"https://schema.org","@graph":[{"@type":["Organization","Person"],"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person","name":"Road to Study - Turkey University Guide for Students","url":"https://roadtostudy.com","logo":{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#logo","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kare-Logo-e1740739634958.png","contentUrl":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kare-Logo-e1740739634958.png","caption":"Road to Study - Turkey University Guide for Students","inLanguage":"en-US","width":"450","height":"445"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#logo"}},{"@type":"WebSite","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#website","url":"https://roadtostudy.com","name":"Road to Study - Turkey University Guide for Students","alternateName":"Road to Study in Turkey","publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/meal-scholarships-in-turkey-2025-how-to-apply.webp","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/meal-scholarships-in-turkey-2025-how-to-apply.webp","width":"2336","height":"1760","caption":"Student reviewing meal scholarship documents with a healthy meal on the table.","inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/turkey-meal-scholarships/#webpage","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/turkey-meal-scholarships/","name":"Meal Scholarships in Turkey 2025: How to Apply?","datePublished":"2025-08-04T14:13:30+03:00","dateModified":"2026-03-15T22:23:10+03:00","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#website"},"primaryImageOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/meal-scholarships-in-turkey-2025-how-to-apply.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Person","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","name":"Murat","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f5b866231ae7aed7a61015846c1f0ab6c5797b065ec200b93c5e9daa87897af?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f5b866231ae7aed7a61015846c1f0ab6c5797b065ec200b93c5e9daa87897af?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","caption":"Murat","inLanguage":"en-US"}},{"@type":"BlogPosting","headline":"Meal Scholarships in Turkey 2025: How to Apply?","keywords":"Scholarships,meal","datePublished":"2025-08-04T14:13:30+03:00","dateModified":"2026-03-15T22:23:10+03:00","articleSection":"Scholarships and Funding","author":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","name":"Murat"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"description":"A guide for students seeking food scholarships in Turkey in 2025: Who&#039;s eligible, how to apply, what to do after winning? Read now!","name":"Meal Scholarships in Turkey 2025: How to Apply?","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/turkey-meal-scholarships/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/turkey-meal-scholarships/#webpage"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/meal-scholarships-in-turkey-2025-how-to-apply.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/turkey-meal-scholarships/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<p class="wp-block-paragraph">One of the most challenging aspects of studying at university in Turkey is the cost of food and accommodation. Even lunch can require a serious budget, especially for students living in big cities. That&#8217;s why <strong><em>dining scholarships</em> offered by universities are a great source of support for both Turkish and international students.</strong></p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">I didn&#8217;t take it too seriously in my first year, but when I started paying 8-10 USD every day in the dining hall, I realized what a mistake I was making by missing out on scholarship applications. In this article, I&#8217;ll tell you the most important details about what food scholarships are, who can get them, when the application dates are, and what to do if you win. Let&#8217;s get started if you&#8217;re ready!</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-are-food-scholarships-who-can-receive-them">What are Food Scholarships, Who Can Receive Them?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Food scholarships are free meals offered to needy students by the <em>Departments of Health, Culture and Sports</em> of universities. Usually one meal a day (mostly lunch) is provided free of charge. This support is available for both Turkish and international students.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="who-gets-food-scholarships">Who gets food scholarships?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">This scholarship usually prioritizes students who:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Financially disadvantaged people</li>



<li>KYK scholarship or loan recipients</li>



<li>Family living in another city and trying to make a living on their own</li>



<li>International students studying abroad in Turkey</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Achievement is not usually a criterion, but some universities may require that the student has not been disciplined.</p>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="food-scholarships-aranan-sartlar-neler">


<h2 class="wp-block-heading wp-block-paragraph">What are the requirements for food scholarships?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Although the requirements of each university vary slightly, the documents generally required are:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Student certificate</li>



<li>Declaration of income (can be obtained via e-Government)</li>



<li>Family status information</li>



<li>Application form</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-does-the-psycho-social-services-branch-directorate-do">What does the Psycho-Social Services Branch Directorate do?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">This unit specifically assesses the situation of students in need. In addition to psychological support, social assistance is also coordinated from here. Especially at universities like <a href="https://sks.akdeniz.edu.tr/tr/beslenme-5728" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mediterranean University</a>, this unit also monitors students who receive food scholarships.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="when-and-how-to-apply-for-the-2025-food-scholarship">When and How to Apply for the 2025 Food Scholarship</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Each university has a different application period, but applications are generally accepted in September-October. Sometimes additional applications are opened in November. You should definitely follow the university&#8217;s website and notice boards.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="2025-food-scholarship-application-dates">2025 food scholarship application dates</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Here are the application dates planned by some universities for 2025:</p>


<figure class="wp-block-table">
<table class="has-fixed-layout">
<thead>
<tr>
<th>University</th>
<th>Application Dates</th>
<th>Scholarship Duration</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>ITU</td>
<td>9 January 2025</td>
<td>9 months (245,48 usd)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Anadolu University</td>
<td>March 2025</td>
<td>1 year</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Bursa Uludağ University</td>
<td>17-October 27, 2024</td>
<td>During the academic year</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Hacettepe University</td>
<td>November 7-14, 2024</td>
<td>1 year</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>KTU</td>
<td>September 25 &#8211; October 13, 2024</td>
<td>1 year</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</figure>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Sources:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><a href="https://sks.itu.edu.tr/haberler/2025/01/09/yemek-ve-yurt-bursu-meal-and-dormitory-scholarship" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ITU SKS Department</a></li>



<li><a href="https://egazete.anadolu.edu.tr/kampus/42935/anadolu-universitesi-ogrenci-yemek-bursu-ile-800-ogrencisinin-daha-yaninda" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Anadolu University</a></li>



<li><a href="https://roadtostudy.com/turkiye-burslari-basvuru-sureci/" data-type="post" data-id="2490">Karadeniz Technical University</a></li>



<li><a href="https://roadtostudy.com/ondokuz-mayis-universitesi-tanitim-rehberi/" data-type="page" data-id="630">Ondokuz Mayıs University</a></li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-the-application-process-works">How the application process works</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The application usually proceeds as follows:</p>



<ol class="wp-block-list">
<li>Go to the relevant portal of the university</li>



<li>Required documents uploaded as PDF or JPEG</li>



<li>Fill out and submit the application form</li>



<li>Evaluation result is announced via email or portal</li>
</ol>


<blockquote class="wp-block-quote">


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Some universities announce application deadlines at the beginning of the year, especially as described in <strong><a class="">Turkey&#8217;s academic calendar and semester planning</a></strong>. Therefore, it is a great advantage to do academic planning well.</p>


</blockquote>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="application-documents-and-things-to-keep-in-mind">Application documents and things to keep in mind</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Documents must be legible, application may be canceled if missing documents are submitted.</li>



<li>It is important not to miss the deadline.</li>



<li>If you are receiving another scholarship from KYK, this should be indicated.</li>
</ul>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-to-do-if-you-win-a-food-scholarship">What to do if you win a food scholarship</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You won the scholarship, great! But the process does not end here. Some students lose their rights because they do not activate the system even though they have won. So there are a few details you should be careful about.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="first-steps-after-winning">First steps after winning</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Go to the student cafeteria with your ID card on the date specified by the university.</li>



<li>If the system recognizes you, you can pass without payment when you swipe your card.</li>



<li>Some universities are switching to a daily QR code entry system, pay attention to this.</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="which-meals-are-valid-is-there-a-daily-limit">Which meals are valid? Is there a daily limit?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">It usually applies to lunch and is limited to one meal.<br>Some universities offer a standard menu of soup, main course, rice/pasta and dessert.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-the-annual-renewal-process-works">How the annual renewal process works</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Food scholarships are usually for 1 year. If you want to continue in 2025-2026, you will need to reapply for the new school year, so you will need to prepare your documents again around September 2025.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="food-scholarship-opportunities-by-universities">Food Scholarship Opportunities by Universities</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Each university&#8217;s food scholarship system works differently. Some offer financial support, while others offer free meals directly at the dining hall. Below are some of the food scholarships offered by some universities.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="istanbul-technical-university-monthly-and-annual-figures">Istanbul Technical University: Monthly and annual figures</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">ITU offers two different options to students in 2025 as part of the food scholarship:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Monthly support:</strong> Approximately <strong>27.6 USD</strong></li>



<li><strong>Annual support (9 months):</strong> Approximately <strong>248.7 USD</strong></li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="anadolu-university-support-for-1830-students">Anadolu University: Support for 1830 students</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">According to the announcement made in March 2025, Anadolu University has provided free food scholarships to a total of <strong>1830 students</strong>. These students can benefit from one meal free of charge every day at the university&#8217;s dining halls on campus.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="ankara-mugla-isparta-and-other-examples">Ankara, Muğla, Isparta and other examples</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Muğla Sıtkı Koçman University</strong>: It offers regular meal support to students in need of social assistance.</li>



<li><strong>Isparta University of Applied Sciences</strong>: Students who applied in the fall of 2024 and were selected began using the scholarship between October 11-14.</li>



<li><strong>Ankara University</strong>: Meal support is provided on a purely need-based basis, with no achievement requirements (<a href="https://sks.ankara.edu.tr/gereksinim-destekleri/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">detailed information</a>).</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For more information about these systems, it is best to follow the <em>Department of Health, Culture and Sports</em> pages of the universities.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="alternative-nutrition-supports-for-students">Alternative Nutrition Supports for Students</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Not every student can win food scholarships. There are also different support systems and smart solutions for those who don&#8217;t win.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="social-aids-provided-by-municipalities-and-associations">Social aids provided by municipalities and associations</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Municipalities and some foundations (such as the Turkish Religious Foundation or the Red Crescent) can provide students with periodic meal cards or food aid. In Istanbul, IBB&#8217;s youth card can offer a discounted meal card service valid in university canteens in some regions.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In addition, some local NGOs that RoadtoStudy cooperates with also provide food aid.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="is-it-cheaper-to-cook-your-own-food-student-experiences">Is it cheaper to cook your own food? Student experiences</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">When I was living in a dormitory, I did my weekly grocery shopping and prepared my own meals. It was much cheaper, especially if you ate staple foods like pasta, eggs and yogurt. But time and kitchen access are essential. The cafeteria is a lifesaver, especially during exam weeks.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="special-diets-vegan-halal-gluten-free-options">Special diets: Vegan, halal, gluten-free options</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Most universities are now offering menus to suit different diets.<br>For example:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Istanbul University organizes vegan/vegetarian days.</li>



<li>Hacettepe and Ege University started to experiment with gluten-free menus.</li>



<li>Almost all universities use halal food certified products.</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Nevertheless, if you have special eating habits, you may be more satisfied with off-campus alternatives.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="city-based-supports-istanbul-ankara-and-others">City Based Supports: Istanbul, Ankara and Others</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Food scholarships are easier to access in some cities. In big cities, competition is high but opportunities are plentiful. In smaller cities, the system may be less intensive but support may be limited.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="is-it-easy-to-access-food-scholarships-in-big-cities">Is it easy to access food scholarships in big cities?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Since the number of students is high in places like Istanbul, Ankara and Izmir, the number of applicants is also high. Although this increases competition, municipal support and private scholarships are more common here.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="advantages-of-small-cities">Advantages of small cities</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Smaller cities such as Karabük, Kırşehir and Muş have fewer applicants, increasing the chances of getting a food scholarship. It is also cheaper to eat out in these cities, so even those who cannot get scholarships have less difficulty.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="benefit-from-food-scholarships-while-studying-in-turkey">Benefit from Food Scholarships While Studying in Turkey!</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">As an incoming or current student, a food scholarship can make a big difference to you. It makes you feel more comfortable not only financially but also psychologically. Being able to focus on your studies without the question &#8220;What am I going to eat today?&#8221; in your head is priceless.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><a class="" href="https://roadtostudy.com">RoadToStudy</a>, we track the food scholarships available to you and provide guidance during the application process.<br>Schedule your calendar and contact us now so you don&#8217;t miss the right time to apply. Even one meal makes a difference!</p>', "wp_published_at" = '2025-08-04T11:13:30Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2026-03-15T19:23:10Z', "featured_image" = '{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/meal-scholarships-in-turkey-2025-how-to-apply.webp","alt":"Student reviewing meal scholarship documents with a healthy meal on the table.","title":"meal-scholarships-in-turkey-2025-how-to-apply"}' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'turkey-meal-scholarships';
