<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Şimdi harekete geçme zamanı.</strong><br>Sağlık sigortanı erkenden hallet, burslara başvur ve <a class="" href="https://roadtostudy.com">Road to Study</a> üzerinden sürecin her adımında destek al. Türkiye’de eğitim alırken sağlık güvencen tam olsun, kafan rahat olsun.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-04-30T13:56:25Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T18:55:51Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/health-insurance-for-international-students-in-turkey.webp","alt":"Health insurance options for international students in Turkey","title":"health-insurance-for-international-students-in-turkey"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'tr' AND "slug" = 'turkiye-saglik-sigortasi-burs' );
