<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="conclusion-now-is-the-time-to-step-up">Conclusion: Now is the Time to Step Up</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you want to participate in student exchange programs in Turkey, all you need to do is a little research and prepare carefully for the applications. There are so many sources of financial support that it is not difficult to realize your dream of education if you get information from the right place at the right time.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-08-04T11:40:31Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T19:23:06Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/guide-to-student-exchange-programs-and-financial-support-in-turkey.webp","alt":"guide-to-student-exchange-programs-and-financial-support-in-turkey","title":"guide-to-student-exchange-programs-and-financial-support-in-turkey"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'student-exchange-financial-support' );
