ersity and foundation support. Apply now!","name":"Scholarships for Disabled Students in Turkey","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/disabled-students-scholarship-turkey/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/disabled-students-scholarship-turkey/#webpage"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/scholarship-opportunities-for-disabled-foreign-students-in-turkey.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/disabled-students-scholarship-turkey/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Turkey is a country that values equal access to education for students with disabilities. If you are an international student with disabilities, you can apply for various scholarships offered by both the state and universities and foundations in Turkey.turkey is a country that values equal access to education for students with disabilities.s a country that values equal access to education for students with disabilitboth the</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">At first, some students think that these supports are only for Turkish citizens, but this is not the case. In recent years, especially the <em>Turkey Scholarships</em> program and special quotas of universities have opened doors for foreign disabled students.</p>


<blockquote class="wp-block-quote">


<blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow">
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Universities are taking serious steps towards physical accessibility. There are many applications such as stair-free entrances, elevator systems and special education technologies. For detailed accessibility practices, be sure to check our article titled <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/">Accessibility for Students with Disabilities in Turkey</a>.</p>
</blockquote>


</blockquote>
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="scholarships-offered-by-the-state-and-universities">Scholarships Offered by the State and Universities</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Turkey Scholarships program is one of the leading scholarships provided by the government. This program provides full scholarships to international students at different levels (undergraduate, graduate, doctoral). Although there is no special quota for students with disabilities, additional support can be requested by reporting the health status during the application process.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Some state and foundation universities also offer special scholarships or services for students with disabilities.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="comparative-scholarship-table">Comparative Scholarship Table</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Below is a brief comparison of a few featured scholarships:</p>


