<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="look-to-the-future-with-hope-for-refugee-and-asylum-seeker-students-in-turkey">Look to the Future with Hope for Refugee and Asylum Seeker Students in Turkey!</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you are reading these lines right now, you may be about to take a big step in your own life. Thanks to scholarship programs for refugee and asylum-seeking students in Turkey, your university dream may be closer than ever.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The application process may seem complicated, but with the right guidance it can be much easier. We at <a class="" href="https://roadtostudy.com">Road to Study</a> are here to offer you advice, guidance and motivation throughout this process.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Reaching the future you dream of is as close as an application. Now is the time to step up.</strong></p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What benefits do asylum seekers get in Turkey?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Asylum seekers in Turkey may access social assistance like food, cash, and education aid through Social Assistance and Solidarity Foundations and municipalities.<a href="https://help.unhcr.org/turkiye/social-economic-and-civil-matters/social-and-financial-assistance/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"></a></p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What is the scholarship allowance in Turkey?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Türkiye Scholarships provide a monthly stipend (e.g., 3,500 TL for undergraduates, 5,000 TL for master’s, 6,500 TL for PhD), plus tuition, housing, and insurance.<a href="https://www.turkiyeburslari.gov.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"></a></p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What is the Catalan scholarship for refugees?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">No specific &#8220;Catalan scholarship&#8221; for refugees exists in available data; however, Spain offers general refugee aid, including education support via UNHCR programs.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What is the Syria scholarship Program in Turkey?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Türkiye Scholarships support Syrian refugees with tuition, accommodation, a monthly stipend, health insurance, and Turkish language courses for higher education.<a href="https://globalcompactrefugees.org/good-practices/higher-education-syrian-youth" target="_blank" rel="noopener"></a></p>', "wp_published_at" = '2025-08-04T10:04:34Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2026-03-15T19:23:16Z', "featured_image" = '{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/scholarship-programs-for-refugee-and-asylum-seeker-students-in-turkey.webp","alt":"Scholarship programs for refugee and asylum seeker students in Turkey","title":"scholarship-programs-for-refugee-and-asylum-seeker-students-in-turkey"}' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'scholarships-for-refugees-and-asylum-seekers-in-turkey';
