description":"International scholarship opportunities for international students studying in Turkey. Application tips and details are now on the blog. Discover now!","name":"International Scholarships in Turkey: Don&#039;t Miss Your Chance","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/international-scholarships-turkey/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/international-scholarships-turkey/#webpage"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/scholarship-opportunities-provided-by-international-organizations-in-turkey.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/international-scholarships-turkey/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>International scholarships enable thousands of students who want to study in Turkey</strong> to achieve their academic dreams. From the European Union to the United Nations, from Fulbright to the Islamic Development Bank, many global institutions offer comprehensive scholarship opportunities to foreign students attending universities in Turkey.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="scholarship-programs-of-the-united-nations-and-affiliated-organizations-in-turkey">Scholarship Programs of the United Nations and Affiliated Organizations in Turkey</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The <strong>international scholarships</strong> offered by the United Nations are particularly inclusive for refugee and disadvantaged students. Organizations such as UNHCR, UNESCO and UNDP offer financial support for students who want to study in Turkey.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Particularly UNHCR scholarships facilitate access to higher education for young people under temporary protection. This makes Turkey preferable in the field of <strong>international scholarships</strong>. These supports, which cover both tuition fees and living expenses throughout university education, make it possible for students to achieve their academic goals.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Below you can see the main types of scholarships offered by some UN organizations:</p>


<figure class="wp-block-table"><a href="https://www.undp.org/tr/turkiye" target="_blank" rel="noopener">UNDP</a>Development ScholarshipsStudents from developing countriesPartial scholarship, educational material support
