<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="scholarship-programs-of-the-united-nations-and-affiliated-organizations-in-turkey">Scholarship Programs of the United Nations and Affiliated Organizations in Turkey</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The <strong>international scholarships</strong> offered by the United Nations are particularly inclusive for refugee and disadvantaged students. Organizations such as UNHCR, UNESCO and UNDP offer financial support for students who want to study in Turkey.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Particularly UNHCR scholarships facilitate access to higher education for young people under temporary protection. This makes Turkey preferable in the field of <strong>international scholarships</strong>. These supports, which cover both tuition fees and living expenses throughout university education, make it possible for students to achieve their academic goals.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Below you can see the main types of scholarships offered by some UN organizations:</p>


