<td>Tourism and environment training</td>
<td>April &#8211; November</td>
</tr>
</thead>
</table>
</figure>
<div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height: 22px;" aria-hidden="true"> </div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" />
<div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height: 22px;" aria-hidden="true"> </div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="opening-a-new-page-in-education-in-turkey-apply-now">Opening a New Page in Education in Turkey: Apply Now!</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Development agency grants not only provide funding, but also introduce you to the cultural and social fabric of <strong>Turkey</strong> in a powerful way. Every educational project you participate in contributes not only academically, but also humanitarian and socially.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="cultural-awareness-and-interaction-with-agencies">Cultural Awareness and Interaction with Agencies</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">While taking part in projects, you will have the opportunity to get to know Turkish culture more closely. Such projects are invaluable for the language learning process, interaction with locals and understanding cultural norms.</p>', "wp_published_at" = '2025-08-05T13:58:15Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2026-03-15T19:23:01Z', "featured_image" = '{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/training-supports-of-development-agencies-in-turkey.webp","alt":"Training support by development agencies in Turkey","title":"training-supports-of-development-agencies-in-turkey"}' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'development-agency-education-support';
