ar-dernegi-burslari/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/mezunlar-dernegi-burslari/#webpage"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/scholarships-provided-by-alumni-associations-in-turkiye.webp"},"inLanguage":"tr","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/mezunlar-dernegi-burslari/#webpage"}}]}]}'), '$.content_html', '<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Türkiye’de eğitim almak isteyen biri olarak burs konusu, belki de düşündüğün en kritik şeylerden biri. Devlet bursları ya da özel vakıf destekleri kadar bilinmese de, “<strong>mezunlar derneği</strong>” bursları da üniversite yaşamında fark yaratabiliyor. Mezunlar, kendi deneyimlerinden yola çıkarak yeni nesil öğrencilere destek olmayı bir sorumluluk olarak görüyor ve bunu ciddi şekilde organize ediyorlar. Hele ki büyük üniversitelerin mezunlar dernekleri, bu konuda oldukça aktif ve cömert.</p>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="mezunlar-dernegi-nedir-ve-neden-onemlidir">Mezunlar Derneği Nedir ve Neden Önemlidir?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Bu dernekler aynı zamanda aktif bağış toplama ve öğrenciye destek sağlama işlevi de görüyor. Kimi zaman tek bir mezunun desteğiyle, kimi zaman ise onlarca mezunun katkısıyla burs fonları oluşturuluyor. Bu burslar da doğrudan ihtiyaç sahibi öğrencilere yönlendiriliyor.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="turkiyedeki-dernek-kulturu-ve-egitimdeki-yeri">Türkiye’deki Dernek Kültürü ve Eğitimdeki Yeri</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özellikle üniversite düzeyindeki kurumların mezunlar dernekleri, hem maddi yardım sağlıyor hem de öğrencilere mentorluk yapıyor. Dernekler sadece parasal değil, sosyal sermaye açısından da güçlü birer kaynak. Mezunlar, öğrencilere staj, iş, hatta barınma konusunda destek olabiliyor. Türkiye’de <a class="">öğrenci dostu restoranlar ve yemekhaneler</a> gibi ekonomik yaşam alanlarına erişimin önemli olduğu bu süreçte, bu tarz destekler altın değerinde.</p>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="turkiyede-en-bilinen-mezunlar-dernegi-burslari">Türkiye’de En Bilinen Mezunlar Derneği Bursları</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="gsumed-burs-programi-galatasaray-universitesi-mezunlar-dernegi">GSÜMED Burs Programı – Galatasaray Üniversitesi </h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><a href="https://gsumed.org/burs-programi/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Galatasaray Üniversitesi Mezunlar Derneği (GSÜMED)</a>, her yıl ihtiyaç sahibi öğrencilere burs sağlıyor. Bu burs, 9 ay boyunca düzenli olarak ödeniyor ve öğrencilerin öğrenim süresince karşılaştığı finansal yükü azaltmayı amaçlıyor. Başvuru koşulları, GSÜMED’in resmi sitesinde duyuruluyor ve genelde her eğitim yılı başında güncelleniyor. Özellikle sosyal bilimler öğrencileri bu burstan yoğun biçimde faydalanıyor.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="odtu-mezunlari-dernegi-burs-ve-yardimlar-komitesi">ODTÜ Mezunları Derneği – Burs ve Yardımlar Komitesi</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><a href="https://www.odtumd.org.tr/burs-ve-yardimlar-komitesi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ankara merkezli olan ODTÜ Mezunları Derneği</a>, her yıl yüzlerce öğrenciye burs sağlıyor. 2024-2025 eğitim yılında belirlenen burs miktarları yaklaşık olarak tam burs için <strong>59 USD</strong>, yarım burs için ise <strong>36 USD</strong> civarında. Başvuru süreci oldukça düzenli işliyor. Öğrencilerin transkript, öğrenci belgesi ve maddi durum beyanı ile derneğe başvurması gerekiyor. Bu başvurular genellikle <strong>Eylül ayında</strong> alınıyor ve değerlendirme süreci titizlikle yürütülüyor.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="cagdas-yasami-destekleme-dernegi-mezunlar-destekli-projeler">Çağdaş Yaşamı Destekleme Derneği </h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Her ne kadar bir “mezunlar derneği” olmasa da <a href="https://www.cydd.org.tr/sayfa/universite-burslari-104/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ÇYDD</a>, mezun bağışlarıyla desteklenen burs projeleriyle benzer bir işlev görüyor. Hergüner Bilgen Özeke Hukuk Bürosu ya da Aresk Kimya gibi kurumlar aracılığıyla verilen burslar sayesinde yüzlerce öğrenciye yıllardır destek sağlanıyor. Bu burslara başvuran öğrenciler genelde sosyoekonomik düzeyi düşük ama akademik başarısı yüksek bireyler oluyor.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">İşte bu bursların kısa özeti bir tabloda:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-table"><table class="has-fixed-layout"><thead><tr><th><strong>Mezunlar Derneği</strong></th><th><strong>Burs Türü</strong></th><th><strong>Süre</strong></th><th><strong>Miktar (Aylık)</strong></th><th><strong>Başvuru Zamanı</strong></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>GSÜMED</td><td>Destek Bursu</td><td>9 Ay</td><td>40–60 USD (değişken)</td><td>Eylül–Ekim</td></tr><tr><td>ODTÜ Mezunları Derneği</td><td>Tam/Yarım</td><td>9 Ay</td><td>36 USD / 59 USD</td><td>Eylül</td></tr><tr><td>ÇYDD</td><td>Proje Bursu</td><td>Değişken</td><td>30–70 USD (bağışa bağlı)</td><td>Tüm yıl</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="mezunlar-dernegi-burslarina-nasil-basvurulur">Mezunlar Derneği Burslarına Nasıl Başvurulur?</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="belgeler-online-formlar-ve-referanslar">Belgeler, Online Formlar ve Referanslar</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Her “<strong>mezunlar derneği</strong>” bursu için farklı evraklar gerekse de genel olarak şunlar istenir: öğrenci belgesi, transkript, gelir belgesi ve kısa bir motivasyon mektubu. Bazı dernekler online form doldurmanızı isterken, bazıları e-posta ile başvuru alır. Referans mektupları ise büyük artı sağlar.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="dikkat-edilmesi-gereken-tarihler-ve-detaylar">Dikkat Edilmesi Gereken Tarihler ve Detaylar</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Başvuru tarihleri dernekten derneğe değişir. Genellikle Eylül ayı başında açılır ve bir ay kadar sürer. Son başvuru tarihine dikkat etmek, belgeleri eksiksiz ve zamanında göndermek çok önemli. Aksi halde başvuru değerlendirilmeye alınmaz.</p>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="yabanci-ogrenciler-icin-mezunlar-dernegi-burslari-mumkun-mu">Yabancı Öğrenciler İçin Mezunlar Derneği Bursları Mümkün mü?</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="uygunluk-sartlari-ve-dil-bariyeri">Uygunluk Şartları ve Dil Bariyeri</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Türkiye’deki çoğu <strong>mezunlar derneği</strong> burs programı, ağırlıklı olarak Türk vatandaşlarına yöneliktir. Bunun temel nedeni, derneklerin bağışçı ağlarının genellikle yerel mezunlardan oluşmasıdır. Ancak bu durum her zaman “hayır” anlamına gelmez. Bazı özel burs programları özellikle uluslararası ilişkiler, kültürel değişim ya da sosyal sorumluluk temalı projelerde yabancı öğrencilere de açık olabilir.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Dil bariyeri de göz önünde bulundurulmalı. Başvurular genellikle Türkçe yapılır. Bu nedenle başvuru formunu doldururken bir Türk arkadaşınızdan ya da danışmandan destek almak işinizi kolaylaştırır. Ayrıca motivasyon mektubunuzu Türkçe yazmanız, değerlendiricilerin sizi daha iyi tanımasına yardımcı olabilir.</p>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="simdi-senin-siran-mezunlar-dernegi-bursuna-basvur-ve-fark-yarat">Mezunlar Derneği Bursuna Başvur ve Fark Yarat</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Bazen küçük bir destek, büyük bir değişimin ilk adımı olur. Türkiye’deki <strong>mezunlar derneği</strong> bursları, yalnızca maddi yardım değil; aynı zamanda ait olma hissi ve dayanışma duygusudur. Bugün burs başvurusunu yapan bir öğrenci, yarının destek veren mezunu olabilir.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">İhtiyacın olan tek şey: doğru derneği bulmak, başvuru belgelerini hazırlamak ve cesaretle sürece adım atmak. Özellikle üniversite hayatının ilk yıllarında bu tarz burslar, hem ekonomik hem de psikolojik olarak seni rahatlatabilir. Bu yüzden şimdi harekete geçme zamanı.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><a class="" href="https://roadtostudy.com">Road to Study</a> olarak biz de eğitim yolculuğunda her adımda yanında olmak istiyoruz. Başvuru yapmadan önce üniversitenin resmi sayfasını ve mezunlar derneğinin duyurularını mutlaka kontrol et. Şansını zorla, çünkü başvurmayan hiçbir burs kazanılmaz!</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"></p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-05-05T07:46:07Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T18:55:31Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/scholarships-provided-by-alumni-associations-in-turkiye.webp","alt":"Scholarships from alumni associations in Turkiye","title":"scholarships-provided-by-alumni-associations-in-turkiye"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'tr' AND "slug" = 'mezunlar-dernegi-burslari' );
UPDATE "ec_posts" SET "source_seo" = '{"title":"Special Scholarships for Female Students in Turkey","description":"Get one step closer to your educational dreams with special scholarship opportunities for female students. Discover government, NGO, and university scholarships now!","robots":"follow, index, max-snippet:-1, max-video-preview:-1, max-image-preview:large","ogTitle":"Special Scholarships for Female Students in Turkey","ogDescription":"Get one step closer to your educational dreams with special scholarship opportunities for female students. Discover government, NGO, and university scholarships now!","ogImage":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/special-scholarship-opportunities-for-female-students-in-turkey-1024x772.webp","twitterCard":"summary_large_image","twitterTitle":"Special Scholarships for Female Students in Turkey","twitterDescription":"Get one step closer to your educational dreams with special scholarship opportunities for female students. Discover government, NGO, and university scholarships now!","canonicalPath":"/en/special-scholarship-for-female-students/","hreflang":[{"hreflang":"tr","href":"/kadin-ogrencilere-ozel-burs/"},{"hreflang":"en","href":"/en/special-scholarship-for-female-students/"}],"jsonLd":[{"@context":"https://schema.org","@graph":[{"@type":["Organization","Person"],"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person","name":"Road to Study - Turkey University Guide for Students","url":"https://roadtostudy.com","logo":{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#logo","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kare-Logo-e1740739634958.png","contentUrl":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kare-Logo-e1740739634958.png","caption":"Road to Study - Turkey University Guide for Students","inLanguage":"en-US","width":"450","height":"445"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#logo"}},{"@type":"WebSite","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#website","url":"https://roadtostudy.com","name":"Road to Study - Turkey University Guide for Students","alternateName":"Road to Study in Turkey","publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/special-scholarship-opportunities-for-female-students-in-turkey.webp","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/special-scholarship-opportunities-for-female-students-in-turkey.webp","width":"2336","height":"1760","caption":"Scholarship opportunities for female students in Turkey","inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/special-scholarship-for-female-students/#webpage","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/special-scholarship-for-female-students/","name":"Special Scholarships for Female Students in Turkey","datePublished":"2025-08-05T17:11:37+03:00","dateModified":"2026-03-15T22:22:56+03:00","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#website"},"primaryImageOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/special-scholarship-opportunities-for-female-students-in-turkey.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Person","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","name":"Murat","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f5b866231ae7aed7a61015846c1f0ab6c5797b065ec200b93c5e9daa87897af?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f5b866231ae7aed7a61015846c1f0ab6c5797b065ec200b93c5e9daa87897af?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","caption":"Murat","inLanguage":"en-US"}},{"@type":"BlogPosting","headline":"Special Scholarships for Female Students in Turkey","keywords":"Special Scholarship,Female Students,Special Scholarship Opportunities","datePublished":"2025-08-05T17:11:37+03:00","dateModified":"2026-03-15T22:22:56+03:00","articleSection":"Scholarships and Funding","author":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","name":"Murat"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"description":"Get one step closer to your educational dreams with special scholarship opportunities for female students. Discover government, NGO, and university scholarships now!","name":"Special Scholarships for Female Students in Turkey","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/special-scholarship-for-female-students/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/special-scholarship-for-female-students/#webpage"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/special-scholarship-opportunities-for-female-students-in-turkey.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/special-scholarship-for-female-students/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The biggest obstacle for many young people dreaming of university is economic hardship. Especially for female students, this process can be more complicated. Fortunately, in Turkey, these programs make a significant difference in the educational journey. In this article, I have compiled many different <strong>special scholarship</strong> opportunities for women students, from government-sponsored options to non-governmental organizations to international students.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="why-women-only-scholarships-matter">Why Women-Only Scholarships Matter</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="equality-in-education-is-still-a-goal">Equality in Education is Still a Goal</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Access to education is still unequal in our country. This is why <strong>special scholarship policies for women students</strong> are not only an economic but also a social necessity. These steps taken to make women more visible in higher education have great significance, especially in disadvantaged regions.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-financial-support-affects-academic-success">How Financial Support Affects Academic Success</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Campus life, textbooks and dormitory fees add up. This is where <strong>special scholarships for female students</strong> come into play, which not only reduces costs but also allows students to focus better on their studies.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="state-and-university-supported-scholarships">State and University Supported Scholarships</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="kyk-scholarship-the-common-option">KYK Scholarship: The Common Option</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">While KYK scholarships are comprehensive, they do not fall under the category of <strong>special scholarships for female students</strong>. However, since social and economic status is taken into account, many women students can indirectly benefit from these scholarships.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="bilkent-university-scholarship-program-for-girls">Bilkent University &#8220;Scholarship Program for Girls&#8221;</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><a href="https://adaybilgi.bilkent.edu.tr/index.php/kizlara-burs-programi/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bilkent&#8217;s &#8220;Scholarship Program for Girls&#8221;</a> is clearly a <strong>special scholarship for female students</strong>. Through this scholarship, academically successful female students can receive uninterrupted support throughout their undergraduate studies. The program is funded by donors and looks at the needs of applicants, not just their achievements.</p>



<blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow">
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For more information, you can also take a look at our article <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/">Women&#8217;s Safety and Precautions in Turkey</a>.</p>
</blockquote>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="support-from-civil-society-organizations">Support from Civil Society Organizations</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="kahev-outstanding-achievement-scholarship">KAHEV Outstanding Achievement Scholarship</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><a href="https://kahev.org.tr/burs/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Women Physicians Education Support Foundation (KAHEV)</a> is a private foundation that offers scholarships exclusively to <strong>women students</strong>, but only through a reference system instead of a traditional application. Students cannot apply directly. Instead, female medical doctors or female dentists who are members of KAHEV should be a reference for the student.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The details of the reference system are as follows:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Each KAHEV member physician can be a reference for a maximum of 3 students in the same academic year.</li>



<li>The student must study in a public school in Turkey or TRNC.</li>



<li>Private school students are only considered if they have 100% scholarship.</li>



<li>The total monthly income of the applicant student&#8217;s family must be below two minimum wages (approximately below 875 USD).</li>



<li>Students who benefit from scholarships other than KYK should not exceed the monthly scholarship limit (approximately 52 USD/month).</li>



<li>Application will be rejected if there is more than one property or more than one vehicle in the family.</li>



<li>Students with cult, congregation, organization connections are excluded from the evaluation.</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>KAHEV, which prioritizes the criteria for special scholarships</strong> for female students, also prioritizes supporting female students from families who have lost their parents or divorced.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="tev-dormitory-scholarships-safe-housing-and-financial-support">TEV Dormitory Scholarships: Safe Housing and Financial Support</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Housing in big cities can be a serious problem for female students, both economically and in terms of safety. <a href="https://www.tev.org.tr/burs-kiz-ogrenci-yurt-burslari/tr/11" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Turkish Education Foundation (TEV)</a> is one of the rare organizations that has created a solution to this need. One of the types of <strong>special scholarships</strong> offered by TEV for women students is &#8220;dormitory scholarships.&#8221;</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="where-are-tev-dormitories-for-girls">Where are TEV Dormitories for Girls?</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">TEV operates four girls&#8217; dormitories in Izmir (Balçova), Ankara and Trabzon. These dormitories stand out not only for their accommodation, but also for their safe environment that supports academic development. Students are admitted to these dormitories in two ways:</p>



<ol class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Fee Based Housing:</strong> Students can live in the dormitory by paying the dormitory fee.</li>



<li><strong>Scholarship Housing:</strong> Female students in financial need and successful female students can stay free of charge and also receive pocket money.</li>
</ol>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">TEV&#8217;s dormitory scholarship is also a <strong>special scholarship</strong> for female students because it is only offered to female students and is selected according to TEV scholarship criteria.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="who-can-apply">Who can apply?</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Conditions that candidates who will apply for scholarship housing must meet:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>T.C. citizenship</li>



<li>Needing financial support</li>



<li>Not receiving a scholarship from another institution (except KYK loan)</li>



<li>Studying at public universities</li>



<li>Not being in open education, foundation universities or distance education programs</li>



<li>Be younger than 25 years old</li>



<li>No disciplinary penalties</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In addition, there must be a distance between the city where the student&#8217;s family is located and the dormitory. In other words, the family must reside outside Izmir for Izmir dormitory and outside Trabzon for Trabzon dormitory.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="scholarship-amounts-and-duration">Scholarship Amounts and Duration</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">TEV also provides monthly pocket money to students who benefit from the scholarship dormitory. For 2024-2025, this amount is <strong>118 USD</strong>. The scholarship lasts for 9 months and can be renewed the following year depending on success.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="open-scholarships-for-international-women-students">Open Scholarships for International Women Students</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="turkey-scholarships-program-ytb">Turkey Scholarships Program (YTB)</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The most popular option for foreign students, Turkey Scholarships is a comprehensive program that covers all expenses.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="special-field-scholarships-for-women">Special Field Scholarships for Women</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Some universities directly offer <strong>special scholarships</strong> for international students. Thanks to such scholarships, especially in fields such as engineering and medicine, you can both study in Turkey and expand your academic network.</p>



<blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow">
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you are an international student, be sure to check out our <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/">Guide for Women Travelers in Turkey</a>.</p>
</blockquote>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="strategies-and-final-advice-for-winning-scholarships">Strategies and Final Advice for Winning Scholarships</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="5-tips-to-make-a-difference-in-your-application">5 Tips to Make a Difference in Your Application</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Preparing a good application often determines the outcome. If you pay attention to these, you will significantly increase your chances:</p>



<ol class="wp-block-list">
<li>Insert your story in your letter of intent</li>



<li>Highlight your history of social responsibility</li>



<li>Source your references from reliable people</li>



<li>Prepare a portfolio</li>



<li>Keep application dates in an Excel file</li>
</ol>


<div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height: 22px;" aria-hidden="true"> </div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" />
<div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height: 22px;" aria-hidden="true"> </div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="now-is-the-time-to-act">Now is the Time to Act!</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you are determined to pursue your education, there is a <strong>special scholarship for female students</strong> to support you. </p>



<blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow">
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You can follow current scholarship applications on <a class="" href="https://roadtostudy.com">Road to Study</a> and get support with our counseling service. The right scholarship can change not only your schooling but also your life.</p>
